# Drop Folder
#
# Drop files here for the AI Employee to process.
# The File System Watcher monitors this folder and creates
# action items in the Needs_Action folder.
#
# Supported file types:
# - Documents: PDF, DOC, DOCX, TXT
# - Spreadsheets: XLS, XLSX, CSV
# - Images: JPG, PNG, GIF, SVG
# - Archives: ZIP, RAR, 7Z
#
# Files are processed based on rules in Company_Handbook.md
